They had been building a clockwork exploration ship, before the
war against the Dread King arose. Now that he was out of the way,
they had completed the ship and were preparing to cast off. But
they needed some people to help them explore any other lands they
may find. So Arorua and I joined them, seeing how it would give
us time to see exotic places and do exotic things..which I will
leave to your imagination again. </font></p>

<p><font size="3">But unfortunately, I made two mistakes. First
of which was a gnomish clockwork. I should have known better,
seeing how clockworks aern't the most reliable. The second
mistake<was that it the ship, which is aptly named the Coral XV, was piloted by gnomes. Leave it to gnomes to run aground on a coral reef that is jutting up 4 feet into the air. So that halted our journey, luckily we were not all that far away from Antonica. So all those that were not repairing the Coral XV left and took up room and board in Freeport. </font></font></p>

<p><font size="3">Which was a difficult task, seeing how nearly
every inn was filled with visitors for the Best of the Best
